{
  "stem": "22047.1",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And so we always, during the summer, went to Portland.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I was-- thoroughly enjoyed Portland, Oregon.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "All the-- the freshness of it, the woods, and the swimming pools, and Jantzen Beach, and-- and the-- the Ferris wheel and the roller coaster there at Jantzen Beach.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we spent a couple of months every summer, almost every summer, going up there.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Leone.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Leone [?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Waite, ?] and her maiden name was Crepps, of German descent.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And my mother eventually, unfortunately, she passed away in her 50s, in 1955, and that was pretty traumatic.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She died of cancer.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were awfully close.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "She-- she spent most of her life as-- I think when I talked to you earlier, that-- that she was a-- I think I said, just a housewife, but that's-- that's a poor use of the word just.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 10,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And she was a housewife and loved to cook, loved to sew, and a very, very tender and loving person.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, they-- they-- most of the time, they-- they weren't strict.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They-- they had a lot of friends, particularly in Santa Barbara.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He being part of the-- of the-- the faculty, since he was the ROTC instructor, they had a lot of friends, played a lot of bridge together with their friends and a lot of entertaining back and forth.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so they, I think they enjoyed each other quite a bit.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She was, as I said, very attached to her mother, so there was that.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I don't know whether that was a-- came between them or not, but in-- in-- in the main, they-- they were well suited for one another.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, I have a-- a sister.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Her name is Betty Cosgrove.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "She's-- she's married to a-- he's a painting contractor.",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
